videos.headline: Western Michigan scores TD on kickoff fumble recovery
videos.description: On the kickoff, Ball State's Justin Hall fumbles the ball and Western Michigan's Obbie Jackson returns it 21 yards for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Wassink connects with Watson for a Broncos' TD
videos.description: Western Michigan's Jon Wassink finds Keishawn Watson in the corner of the end zone for a 12-yard score to extend the Broncos' lead.

videos.headline: WMU scores on rushing TD from Bellamy
videos.description: Bronco's LeVante Bellamy runs to the outside for a 7-yard score to stretch Western Michigan's lead.

videos.headline: Western Michigan tacks on 52-yard passing TD
videos.description: Jon Wassink drops back and goes deep finding Keishawn Watson for a big score adding to the Knight's lead.
